k reclaims barbarism's edge and proposes it as a useful theoretical tool.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 23. Jul 2020) 0aCivilization. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUP Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311070420440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9780804785372zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804785372423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780804785372.jpg  a978-3-11-070420-4  SUP Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles